{
  "stem": "21812.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was not able to-- very difficult for her to discuss her feelings with me, maybe with other people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "With me, she-- she really never-- because she was very tearful and she would-- afraid of breaking down.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and so she just kept it all to herself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She-- she was working a domestic at the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my uncle and aunt who had come here, were-- they still-- they had a little-- had a-- we had a little house.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They-- they-- she was working as a domestic, and so I didn't see much of her, because she worked.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then on Sundays-- and I-- I-- I lived-- initially, I lived with a-- one of my father's brothers in Bayonne, New Jersey.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And another brother was in Perth Amboy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the third one lived in the Bronx.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there was also a-- a-- another nephew-- no, an aunt, I think, of my father's.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But they were also-- but she was also the same age as the brothers for whatever reason.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't know what the relationship was, but she was there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so first I lived with my-- with one of his brothers who had four children.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I didn't feel very comfortable there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- and then I-- and also, you know, I-- it took me years to get over the anger that I felt for my uncles, his brothers, not to have sent him the affidavit.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He really appealed to them, and they-- they would have saved his life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I felt very, very angry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It took me a long time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So I-- I put all that anger on them.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
